{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-031","title":"Sentence 31","sectionId":"sentences-031","sectionTitle":"Sentence 31-40","pageStart":213,"pageEnd":221,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":66,"duplicateEntryCount":12,"pages":[{"number":213,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 31"},{"type":"text","text":"Even before the discovery of germs, beliefs that disease spread by"},{"type":"text","text":"“miasmas” （noxious forms of bad air） prompted attention to sewers"},{"type":"text","text":"and open garbage."},{"type":"text","text":"甚至在发现细菌以前，疾病通过“瘴气”（有毒的恶性气体）传"},{"type":"text","text":"播的观点就已激起人们对排水沟和露天垃圾的关注。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Beliefs prompted attention。句首的介词短语even"},{"type":"text","text":"before the discovery of germs作时间状语，beliefs后的that引导同位语从"},{"type":"text","text":"句解释说明beliefs。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"germ /dʒɜːrm/ n. 微生物；细菌；萌芽","headword":"germ"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 本身是词根，意为“芽”"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 microorganism n. 微生物"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 germfree a. 无菌的"},{"type":"entry","text":"noxious /ˈnɑːkʃəs/ a. 有害的；有毒的","headword":"noxious"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 nox（毒）+ious→有毒的"}]},{"number":214,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"参考 nocuous a. 有毒的；有害的"},{"type":"entry","text":"prompt /prɑːmpt/ vt. 促使；激起","headword":"prompt"},{"type":"definition","text":"a. 敏捷的；迅速的"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 pro（向前）+mpt（=empt拿）→向前拿→促进，推动"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 promptly ad. 迅速地"},{"type":"text","text":"promptness n. 敏捷，迅速"},{"type":"entry","text":"attention /əˈtenʃn/ n. 注意力；关心","headword":"attention"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 at+tent（伸展）+ion（名词后缀）→听得伸长了脖子→注意"},{"type":"text","text":"力"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 pay attention to 注意；重视"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“排水”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"drainage /ˈdreɪnɪdʒ/ n. 排水；污水","headword":"drainage"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 drainage ditch 排水沟"},{"type":"text","text":"drainage hole 排水孔"},{"type":"text","text":"drainage system 排水系统"},{"type":"entry","text":"sewage /ˈsuːɪdʒ/ n. 污水；下水道","headword":"sewage"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 sewage disposal 污水处理"},{"type":"text","text":"sewage engineering 污水排放工程"},{"type":"entry","text":"sewer /ˈsuːər/ n. 下水道；阴沟","headword":"sewer"},{"type":"text","text":"与“毒气”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"detoxify /ˌdiːˈtɑːksɪfaɪ/ vt. 解毒","headword":"detoxify"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 detoxification n. 解毒"}]},{"number":215,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"poison /ˈpɔɪzn/ n. 毒","headword":"poison"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 poisonous a. 有毒的"},{"type":"entry","text":"toxin /ˈtɑːksɪn/ n. 毒素","headword":"toxin"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 toxic a. 有毒的"},{"type":"text","text":"toxication n. 中毒"},{"type":"text","text":"toxicology n. 毒物学"},{"type":"text","text":"与“疾病”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"acne /ˈækni/ n. 粉刺","headword":"acne"}]},{"number":216,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"alcoholism /ˈælkəhɔːlɪzəm/ n. 酒精中毒","headword":"alcoholism"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 chronic alcoholism 慢性酒精中毒"},{"type":"entry","text":"anemia /əniːmiə/ n. 贫血，贫血症","headword":"anemia"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 nutritional anemia 营养性贫血"},{"type":"entry","text":"appendicitis /əˌpendəˈsaɪtɪs/ n. 阑尾炎；盲肠炎","headword":"appendicitis"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 appendix n. 阑尾；附录"},{"type":"entry","text":"arthritis /ɑːrˈθraɪtɪs/ n. 关节炎","headword":"arthritis"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 arthritic a. 关节炎的"},{"type":"entry","text":"asthenia /æs'θinɪə/ n. 虚弱","headword":"asthenia"},{"type":"entry","text":"bruise /bruːz/ n./v. 淤伤","headword":"bruise"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 bruising n. 挫伤"},{"type":"text","text":"bruised a. 挫伤的"},{"type":"entry","text":"bulimia /buˈlɪmiə/ n. 暴食症","headword":"bulimia"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 bulimic a. 暴食的"},{"type":"entry","text":"cancer /ˈkænsər/ n. 癌","headword":"cancer"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 breast cancer 乳腺癌"}]},{"number":217,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"caries /ˈkeriːz/ n. 龋