rd":"feeble"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 feebleness n. 虚弱"},{"type":"entry","text":"fracture /ˈfræktʃər/ n. 骨折","headword":"fracture"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 fractured a. 骨折的"},{"type":"entry","text":"freckle /ˈfrekl/ n. 痣；雀斑","headword":"freckle"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 ephelis n. 痣；雀斑"},{"type":"entry","text":"gastritis /ɡæˈstraɪtɪs/ n. 胃炎","headword":"gastritis"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 gastric a. 胃的"},{"type":"text","text":"heart disease 心脏病"},{"type":"text","text":"heat stroke 中暑"},{"type":"entry","text":"hives /haɪvz/ n. 荨麻疹","headword":"hives"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 urticaria n. 荨麻疹"}]},{"number":219,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"hypertension /ˌhaɪpərˈtenʃn/ n. 高血压","headword":"hypertension"},{"type":"note","text":"反义 hypotension n. 低血压"},{"type":"entry","text":"incubation /ˌɪŋkjuˈbeɪʃn/ n. 潜伏期","headword":"incubation"},{"type":"entry","text":"indigestion /ˌɪndɪˈdʒestʃən/ n. 消化不良","headword":"indigestion"},{"type":"entry","text":"inflammation /ˌɪnfləˈmeɪʃn/ n. 炎症","headword":"inflammation"},{"type":"entry","text":"leukemia /luːˈkiːmiə/ n. （肿瘤）白血病","headword":"leukemia"},{"type":"text","text":"mad cow disease 疯牛病"},{"type":"entry","text":"malaria /məˈleriə/ n. 疟疾","headword":"malaria"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 falciparum malaria 恶性疟；热带疟"},{"type":"entry","text":"malnutrition /ˌmælnuːˈtrɪʃn/ n. 营养不良","headword":"malnutrition"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 malnourished a. 营养不良的"},{"type":"entry","text":"nausea /ˈnɔːziə/ n. 恶心","headword":"nausea"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 nauseous a. 恶心的；想吐的"},{"type":"entry","text":"nearsightedness /ˌnɪrˈsaɪtɪdnəs/ n. 近视","headword":"nearsightedness"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 myopia n. 近视"},{"type":"entry","text":"nervousness /ˈnɜːrvəsnəs/ n. 神经过敏，紧张不安","headword":"nervousness"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 nervosity n. 神经过敏"},{"type":"entry","text":"perturbed /pərˈtɜːrbd/ a. 烦躁不安的","headword":"perturbed"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 perturbation n. 不安；扰动"},{"type":"entry","text":"pneumonia /nuːˈmoʊniə/ n. 肺炎","headwo